275
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:47,460
say stupid words on purpose

276
00:13:48,180 --> 00:13:49,540
and made fun of me.

277
00:13:55,860 --> 00:13:56,580
Danshu,

278
00:13:58,500 --> 00:13:59,460
what were you like at home

279
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:01,580
before you came to the palace?

280
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:05,300
Have you been naughty

281
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:07,460
and willful before?

282
00:14:10,900 --> 00:14:11,900
Of course.

283
00:14:12,220 --> 00:14:13,700
Otherwise why would I go to the academy

284
00:14:13,700 --> 00:14:15,540
in man’s clothing to attend lectures
in my brother’s name?

285
00:14:18,540 --> 00:14:19,180
True.

286
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:20,860
You are not a common girl,

287
00:14:21,540 --> 00:14:23,300
so your mischievousness is also quite unique.

288
00:14:25,660 --> 00:14:27,820
But in the whole world,

289
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:30,180
we are the last persons

290
00:14:30,180 --> 00:14:31,420
to misbehave.

291
00:14:35,380 --> 00:14:36,100
Just now

292
00:14:36,380 --> 00:14:37,820
I said you were wrong about one thing.

293
00:14:37,980 --> 00:14:41,060
You said Fan Zhongyan

294
00:14:41,900 --> 00:14:42,940
can’t match with Lv Yijian.

295
00:14:44,180 --> 00:14:45,060
Not exactly.

296
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:04,220
Yu Jing was relieved of his post by Lv Yijian

297
00:15:05,380 --> 00:15:09,260
for defending Fan Zhongyan.

298
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:10,500
The whole court burst into an uproar.

299
00:15:10,980 --> 00:15:12,620
Yin Zhu wrote a letter immediately

300
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:15,020
claiming that he is the real close friend

301
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:15,980
of Fan Zhongyan.

302
00:15:16,780 --> 00:15:18,100
If even Yu Jing who

303
00:15:18,180 --> 00:15:19,820
had no personal acquaintance with Fan Zhongyan

304
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:22,860
was regarded one his faction

305
00:15:23,100 --> 00:15:24,260
just because he wrote some proposals
for the sake of justice,

306
00:15:24,660 --> 00:15:27,140
then he wants to be punished too
for being one of Mr. Fan’s faction.

307
00:15:28,660 --> 00:15:30,340
Prime Minister Lv is being arbitrary.

308
00:15:31,580 --> 00:15:33,580
The punishment for Yu Jing and Yin Zhu

309
00:15:33,580 --> 00:15:34,540
is farfetched already,

310
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:37,100
and now he’s releasing strict rules

311
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:38,020
from the two offices

312
00:15:38,180 --> 00:15:39,820
forbidding people to
talk about issues out of their range.

313
00:15:40,180 --> 00:15:41,900
Only Censors can write proposals about this,

314
00:15:41,900 --> 00:15:42,820
blocking the access of voices and opinions.

315
00:15:45,100 --> 00:15:47,180
the Censor Gao Ruone

316
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:50,300
is supposed to correct Prime Minister’s mistakes,

317
00:15:50,980 --> 00:15:52,140
but now he clings to Lv Yijian,

318
00:15:52,700 --> 00:15:53,740
instead of correcting him,

319
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:56,780
he’s now saying Fan Zhongyan earned his punishment.

320
00:15:57,460 --> 00:15:59,340
Naturally, this irritated the uprights
at the court.

321
00:16:00,980 --> 00:16:02,020
Look at this letter

322
00:16:02,420 --> 00:16:04,260
from Ouyang Xiu.

323
00:16:07,420 --> 00:16:09,500
My mother is old now,

324
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:11,940
which makes me value my job.

325
00:16:13,820 --> 00:16:15,340
Let’s say,

326
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:18,460
it would be natural

327
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:20,260
if he chose not to say anything to save his job.

328
00:16:20,860 --> 00:16:23,220
The uprights won’t blame him

329
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:24,620
thinking that

330
00:16:24,620 --> 00:16:25,540
he’s just a blockhead.

331
00:16:25,740 --> 00:16:27,180
They won’t force him to be a person of virtue.

332
00:16:28,020 --> 00:16:28,940
But instead,

333
00:16:28,940 --> 00:16:30,380
to hide his weakness,

334
00:16:30,820 --> 00:16:32,220
he preened himself

335
00:16:32,820 --> 00:16:34,860
for reinforcing that Fan Zhongyan
should be deposed.

336
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:36,780
What a shameless man he is!

337
00:16:39,260 --> 00:16:39,900
How’s it?

338
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:43,860
Complete and vivid.

339
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:46,300
Impressive indeed.

340
00:16:48,380 --> 00:16:49,260
This article will be

341
00:16:49,260 --> 00:16:50,460
wide-spread among

342
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:51,620
scholars and men of letters.

343
00:16:52,010 --> 00:16:54,060
People say Mr. Gao is disgraceful.

344
00:16:54,540 --> 00:16:57,380
You can only see his court board, not his face.

345
00:16:58,380 --> 00:17:00,980
All the other four gentlemen acclaim Fan a man
of virtue, but Gao says he’s a worthless man.

346
00:17:01,420 --> 00:17:04,180
You can fool people with slander, but not the God.

347
00:17:04,580 --> 00:17:06,180
What a bad man!

348
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:08,100
Gao Ruone, this idiot

349
00:17:08,260 --> 00:17:09,460
might have saved his job,

350
00:17:09,620 --> 00:17:11,620
But the letter

351
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:12,860
from Ouyang,

352
00:17:13,020 --> 00:17:15,140
plus the poem

353
00:17:15,220 --> 00:17:17,140
written by Cai Junmo

354
00:17:17,460 --> 00:17:18,860
I believe his reputation

355
00:17:18,900 --> 00:17:20,660
is now ruined forever.

356
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:22,620
Can’t Fan Zhongyan

357
00:17:22,620 --> 00:17:23,900
contend with Lv Yijian?

358
00:17:31,060 --> 00:17:31,940
In terms of

359
00:17:33,300 --> 00:17:35,140
quality, position,

360
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:36,740
friends and fellowships,

361
00:17:37,300 --> 00:17:38,860
Fan Zhongyan can’t compare with
the Prime Minister at all.

362
00:17:39,580 --> 00:17:40,900
But what he did

363
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:43,140
is following the course of Confucianism

364
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:44,100
and is believed by scholars for all time.

365
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:46,340
Then his root

366
00:17:47,060 --> 00:17:49,540
is the scholars across the country
believing in Confucianism

367
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:51,060
who can never be left behind.

368
00:17:56,660 --> 00:17:58,220
For someone like Fan Zhongyan,

369
00:17:59,140 --> 00:18:01,100
it doesn’t matter if he

370
00:18:01,420 --> 00:18:03,100
stays in the Capital or some border town,

371
00:18:04,420 --> 00:18:05,780
at the court or in some village.

372
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:07,420
He’s not one of those

373
00:18:07,420 --> 00:18:09,300
who can be constrained
by personal interests or gains.

374
00:18:12,180 --> 00:18:14,660
The more frustration he has encountered,
the more unafraid he becomes,

375
00:18:15,620 --> 00:18:17,500
the more renowned he will be
as a man of noble character,

376
00:18:17,860 --> 00:18:19,260
and the more vigor of people at the court

377
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:20,740
and across the country

378
00:18:20,740 --> 00:18:22,020
he can arouse!

379
00:18:23,060 --> 00:18:24,180
Trusting and using both of them

380
00:18:24,180 --> 00:18:25,100
don’t mean they both have to

381
00:18:25,100 --> 00:18:26,060
serve the country at the court.

382
00:18:27,820 --> 00:18:29,780
As long as they can contribute to the country,

383
00:18:29,780 --> 00:18:30,900
and the people,

384
00:18:31,260 --> 00:18:32,300
anywhere

385
00:18:32,300 --> 00:18:34,540
can be their home to stay.

386
00:18:37,060 --> 00:18:38,580
Oh, you just said

387
00:18:38,740 --> 00:18:40,220
you came here for family businesses.

388
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:42,740
Any trouble from the harem

389
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:43,900
that even you can’t solve?

390
00:18:44,940 --> 00:18:46,580
If you were not a girl,

391
00:18:46,660 --> 00:18:48,180
you should be a general or a minister

392
00:18:48,260 --> 00:18:49,980
with your vision and talents.

393
00:18:51,260 --> 00:18:52,580
I would like to bother you

394
00:18:53,460 --> 00:18:54,940
to manage all the trifles of the harem.

395
00:18:56,300 --> 00:18:57,260
Why do you keep

396
00:18:57,260 --> 00:18:58,900
making fun of me today?

397
00:18:59,980 --> 00:19:01,460
I meant what I said.

398
00:19:04,700 --> 00:19:06,860
That family business is not a trouble,

399
00:19:07,180 --> 00:19:08,260
but a good thing actually.

400
00:19:09,740 --> 00:19:10,940
But it’s not confirmed yet.

401
00:19:13,740 --> 00:19:15,340
Yesterday Madam Miao told me

402
00:19:16,460 --> 00:19:17,620
she might be pregnant.

403
00:19:19,380 --> 00:19:21,860
I wanted to ask a physician to…

404
00:19:22,580 --> 00:19:23,500
What did you say?

405
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:27,300
Xinhe is pregnant?

406
00:19:30,180 --> 00:19:31,540
Madam Miao told me yesterday.

407
00:19:35,500 --> 00:19:37,060
Ask Physician Wang from the Imperial Hospital

408
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:38,100
to feel the pulse of Madam Miao

409
00:19:38,380 --> 00:19:39,940
in the Pavilion of Phoenix.

410
00:19:40,300 --> 00:19:40,980
Go!

411
00:19:48,980 --> 00:19:49,915
- Liaozi!- Yes, Your Majesty.

412
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:50,500
Liaozi!

413
00:19:50,860 --> 00:19:52,180
Go to see Xinhe with me now!

414
00:19:52,780 --> 00:19:54,020
I’ve been hoping for having a baby with her

415
00:19:54,260 --> 00:19:55,420
for 5 years.

416
00:20:36,980 --> 00:20:37,940
Your Majesty,

417
00:20:38,540 --> 00:20:40,420
she’s doing very well.

418
00:20:40,860 --> 00:20:43,380
She’s pregnant for 4 months.

419
00:20:43,820 --> 00:20:46,740
Both of them are healthy.

420
00:20:49,260 --> 00:20:50,020
Good.

421
00:20:52,020 --> 00:20:53,340
You have excellent medical skills.

422
00:20:55,580 --> 00:20:57,460
Award Physician Wang

423
00:20:57,460 --> 00:20:58,420
with a pair of ink stones and Ruyi.

424
00:20:59,860 --> 00:21:00,980
Thank you, Your Majesty.

425
00:21:02,060 --> 00:21:02,900
If you’ll excuse me.

426
00:21:20,140 --> 00:21:21,500
You are good at hiding it.

427
00:21:22,940 --> 00:21:24,100
You must have known for long.

428
00:21:24,260 --> 00:21:25,780
Why didn’t you tell me?

429
00:21:27,020 --> 00:21:29,180
Last month, I visited you twice,

430
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:31,740
and every time you refused to

431
00:21:31,740 --> 00:21:32,620
get close to me

432
00:21:32,620 --> 00:21:33,460
saying that you caught a flu
and didn’t want to spread to me.

433
00:21:33,460 --> 00:21:34,420
You must’ve known by then?

434
00:21:35,420 --> 00:21:36,540
Why did you keep it from me for so long?

435
00:21:38,860 --> 00:21:40,940
You’ve been waiting for a son for so long,

436
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:45,100
and before there were ladies who got pregnant

437
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:46,820
but then lost their babies.

438
00:21:48,340 --> 00:21:51,780
I didn’t want you to be disappointed again.

439
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:57,260
How can you be the same

440
00:21:57,260 --> 00:21:58,420
as them?

441
00:21:59,780 --> 00:22:01,700
You are my family,

442
00:22:04,300 --> 00:22:05,020
Xinhe,

443
00:22:08,100 --> 00:22:09,220
I am so happy.

444
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:12,420
Since 6 years ago

445
00:22:15,300 --> 00:22:17,420
when I heard my mother deceased,

446
00:22:19,740 --> 00:22:21,380
I’ve never been so happy before.

447
00:22:41,900 --> 00:22:42,900
What are you doing?

448
00:22:43,260 --> 00:22:45,860
This is the first royal son.

449
00:22:45,860 --> 00:22:48,300
He should be taken care of by us!

450
00:22:49,060 --> 00:22:50,860
By us!

451
00:22:50,900 --> 00:22:53,140
- I just want to stay with His Majesty
for my whole life. - Give him to us!

452
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:55,620
I just want to have sons and daughters with him

453
00:22:56,860 --> 00:22:58,740
She’s a girl, not a son.

454
00:22:59,260 --> 00:23:00,180
Liar!

455
00:23:00,180 --> 00:23:02,260
You are throwing the court into disorder.

456
00:23:02,460 --> 00:23:03,460
Give him to me!

457
00:23:03,460 --> 00:23:05,180
He is a son!

458
00:23:05,380 --> 00:23:06,340
Give him to us!

459
00:23:07,780 --> 00:23:08,700
Give him to us!

460
00:23:08,700 --> 00:23:09,420
Liar!

461
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:10,700
She’s a girl!

462
00:23:31,700 --> 00:23:34,260
Madam, you had a bad dream?

463
00:23:34,260 --> 00:23:35,780
= Lu Si =

464
00:23:39,140 --> 00:23:40,300
I made a wish before

465
00:23:41,380 --> 00:23:43,220
to have a son with His Majesty,

466
00:23:44,660 --> 00:23:48,100
to extend the royal family of Song.

467
00:23:50,780 --> 00:23:51,660
I’m wondering

468
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:56,220
if I want to change my wish,

469
00:23:58,580 --> 00:24:00,380
will I be blamed?

470
00:24:15,820 --> 00:24:16,700
Don’t worry, sir,

471
00:24:16,780 --> 00:24:17,660
you are not late.

472
00:24:20,420 --> 00:24:21,780
I’m here early.

473
00:24:35,860 --> 00:24:38,140
Can we wait a second

474
00:24:38,620 --> 00:24:39,500
before we start the lecture today?

475
00:24:45,580 --> 00:24:46,220
Sir.

476
00:24:49,780 --> 00:24:51,540
I wasn’t listening just now.

477
00:24:52,460 --> 00:24:53,220
Somehow

478
00:24:53,220 --> 00:24:55,340
I thought of the snow night years ago.

479
00:24:55,740 --> 00:24:57,060
The second day,

480
00:24:57,820 --> 00:24:58,980
I went to your place in the morning

481
00:24:59,140 --> 00:25:00,340
to teach you The Legend of
Spring and Autumn Century.

482
00:25:00,740 --> 00:25:02,100
But you told me

483
00:25:02,780 --> 00:25:05,300
if we can start a little bit later

484
00:25:05,620 --> 00:25:07,060
and pick some winter sweet first.

485
00:25:10,060 --> 00:25:10,820
Yes, I remember.

486
00:25:11,500 --> 00:25:14,260
It’s because you told me

487
00:25:14,540 --> 00:25:16,340
how to take and preserve

488
00:25:16,340 --> 00:25:17,300
the snow on the petals and press it to ice

489
00:25:17,500 --> 00:25:19,540
with the winter sweet

490
00:25:19,860 --> 00:25:21,500
and use it to make cold drink in the summer.

491
00:25:21,820 --> 00:25:22,460
You also told me

492
00:25:22,620 --> 00:25:24,580
the dessert made with the pistil of winter sweet.

493
00:25:25,860 --> 00:25:26,860
It sounded so attractive,

494
00:25:27,620 --> 00:25:29,500
so I wanted to ask you

495
00:25:29,780 --> 00:25:31,460
to collect some snow and flowers first,

496
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:32,940
then managed to let you teach me

497
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:34,540
how to make the dessert.

498
00:25:35,260 --> 00:25:36,020
Back then,

499
00:25:36,420 --> 00:25:37,860
I really thought

500
00:25:38,340 --> 00:25:40,620
you wanted to see flowers and create poems.

501
00:25:41,340 --> 00:25:43,580
So what you were actually thinking about is food.

502
00:25:45,620 --> 00:25:47,460
I managed to persuade you,

503
00:25:47,700 --> 00:25:49,540
but didn’t expected Her Majesty came

504
00:25:49,820 --> 00:25:50,940
and criticized me.

505
00:25:51,580 --> 00:25:53,500
I couldn’t go to the garden in the snow,

506
00:25:53,740 --> 00:25:54,420
and instead

507
00:25:54,420 --> 00:25:55,980
I was punished to transcribe
The Spring and Autumn Annals.

508
00:25:58,580 --> 00:26:00,020
This is all my fault.

509
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:03,900
I was the prince’s subordinate,

510
00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:08,460
but I couldn’t give up the leisure
and enjoyment in life.

511
00:26:09,180 --> 00:26:10,580
I failed to perform my duty.

512
00:26:12,860 --> 00:26:15,540
You are always graceful
with different interests in life.

513
00:26:17,020 --> 00:26:18,260
So I want to

514
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:22,140
plan with you

515
00:26:24,700 --> 00:26:25,660
to skip the class again.

516
00:26:32,580 --> 00:26:33,540
About princess’s name

517
00:26:34,140 --> 00:26:36,220
and gifts for her,

518
00:26:36,540 --> 00:26:38,900
I need your opinions.

519
00:26:38,940 --> 00:26:39,980
Princess?

520
00:26:40,180 --> 00:26:41,140
I’ve come up

521
00:26:41,140 --> 00:26:42,460
with a bunch of a prince’s names.

522
00:26:42,700 --> 00:26:44,860
I’ve given them to scholars

523
00:26:44,860 --> 00:26:46,460
of the Imperial Academy for consideration.

524
00:26:48,180 --> 00:26:49,260
I’m almost at my 30s.

525
00:26:50,100 --> 00:26:52,220
Surely I want to have a son

526
00:26:52,820 --> 00:26:54,300
and take him with me

527
00:26:54,660 --> 00:26:56,060
when worshiping ancestors.

528
00:26:58,100 --> 00:26:59,500
But personally,

529
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:01,620
I really want to have a princess.

530
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:07,380
A princess doesn’t need to manage the country,

531
00:27:08,060 --> 00:27:09,620
or to shoulder the joy and sorrow of the people.

532
00:27:10,020 --> 00:27:11,580
She just needs to be spoiled by me.

533
00:27:12,740 --> 00:27:14,980
I can let her enjoy

534
00:27:15,220 --> 00:27:16,900
all the fun and happiness

535
00:27:17,780 --> 00:27:19,660
I missed.

536
00:27:28,860 --> 00:27:29,780
The gifts

537
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:32,220
sent here few days ago,

538
00:27:32,820 --> 00:27:34,140
don’t you take a look at them?

539
00:27:36,940 --> 00:27:37,940
Actually Madam Xu

540
00:27:37,940 --> 00:27:39,860
doesn’t know what she should do

541
00:27:40,060 --> 00:27:40,980
with those gifts and people who sent them.

542
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:42,740
If she refused to take the gifts,

543
00:27:42,940 --> 00:27:44,500
she would offend them on your behalf.

544
00:27:50,460 --> 00:27:51,180
Madam,

545
00:27:51,540 --> 00:27:52,900
Huan from the Hall of Peace

546
00:27:52,900 --> 00:27:54,180
came and said

547
00:27:54,420 --> 00:27:56,340
the Empress’s cousin came back from work

548
00:27:56,460 --> 00:27:58,340
and sent some fresh vegetables and fish.

549
00:27:58,660 --> 00:27:59,420
She sent them

550
00:27:59,420 --> 00:28:00,780
= Lan Que =
to the Imperial Kitchen to be cooked

551
00:28:00,860 --> 00:28:02,060
and said she’ll bring the dishes here

552
00:28:02,060 --> 00:28:03,420
to have breakfast with you.

553
00:28:05,380 --> 00:28:07,100
Go to fetch my

554
00:28:07,500 --> 00:28:08,580
Osmanthus cake,

555
00:28:08,860 --> 00:28:09,940
pine nut cake,

556
00:28:10,020 --> 00:28:11,220
jujube paste walnut cookie,

557
00:28:11,900 --> 00:28:13,140
and candied plums.

558
00:28:13,140 --> 00:28:13,900
Take them all.

559
00:28:15,300 --> 00:28:15,940
And the snow water

560
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:17,340
from last year preserved in the silver bottle.

561
00:28:17,620 --> 00:28:18,620
Use it to make some tea.

562
00:28:18,820 --> 00:28:19,260
Yes, Madam.

563
00:28:23,940 --> 00:28:25,260
All these names we came up with

564
00:28:26,220 --> 00:28:27,260
are still not good enough to me.

565
00:28:29,140 --> 00:28:30,180
They are all beautiful names

566
00:28:30,180 --> 00:28:31,660
with good implied meaning.

567
00:28:32,060 --> 00:28:33,900
They deserve any

568
00:28:33,900 --> 00:28:35,300
beautiful and smart girl in the world.

569
00:28:38,820 --> 00:28:40,060
I am being too picky.

570
00:28:41,660 --> 00:28:42,820
Your Majesty’s daughter

571
00:28:43,260 --> 00:28:45,060
is not only a tender and beautiful girl,

572
00:28:45,300 --> 00:28:46,780
the apple in your eyes,

573
00:28:47,140 --> 00:28:48,900
but the princess of the whole country.

574
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:52,020
Your Majesty don’t think these names
match with the princess,

575
00:28:52,460 --> 00:28:54,900
because they only contain the meaning of splendor,

576
00:28:55,260 --> 00:28:56,900
richness and luckiness,

577
00:28:58,100 --> 00:29:00,860
but not the broadness of the princess.

578
00:29:16,460 --> 00:29:17,180
Xinhe,

579
00:29:18,020 --> 00:29:19,220
why do you look unwell?

580
00:29:21,660 --> 00:29:23,260
Didn’t sleep well last night.

581
00:29:26,940 --> 00:29:28,180
Should I send you an imperial doctor

582
00:29:28,180 --> 00:29:28,820
to have a look?

583
00:29:30,900 --> 00:29:32,060
Don’t bother, Your Highness.

584
00:29:32,380 --> 00:29:33,660
I’m not that delicate.

585
00:29:34,020 --> 00:29:35,340
You don’t need to make a fuss about it.

586
00:29:38,180 --> 00:29:38,980
Xinhe,

587
00:29:40,300 --> 00:29:41,100
what’s wrong?

588
00:29:44,260 --> 00:29:45,580
You have any troubles?

589
00:29:51,780 --> 00:29:54,220
The Assistant Prefectural Magistrate of Sizhou,
Chen Hui wrote a proposal saying

590
00:29:55,060 --> 00:29:57,980
recently, Collator Cai Xiang

591
00:29:58,500 --> 00:30:01,020
= Xia Song, courtesy name Ziqiao =
wrote poems to taunt with the court,

592
00:30:01,860 --> 00:30:03,820
and gave them to businessman to print and publish

593
00:30:04,020 --> 00:30:05,860
to the market.

594
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:09,020
It became the topic of conversation

595
00:30:09,100 --> 00:30:12,260
among the people and even envoys
of other countries.

596
00:30:13,740 --> 00:30:15,220
This disgraceful behavior

597
00:30:15,780 --> 00:30:17,460
humiliated main officials at the court

598
00:30:17,500 --> 00:30:19,420
and ruined the reputation of the court.

599
00:30:20,340 --> 00:30:22,580
If we don’t punish him severely

600
00:30:22,860 --> 00:30:25,260
it will encourage the evil

601
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:29,220
that anyone can criticize the court,

602
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:32,700
which will surely hurt our prestige.

603
00:30:45,020 --> 00:30:46,180
I have a question

604
00:30:46,540 --> 00:30:48,260
to Mr. Xia.

605
00:30:52,180 --> 00:30:53,580
Yes, Censor Han.

606
00:30:55,740 --> 00:30:57,060
The Assistant Prefectural Magistrate of Sizhou

607
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:58,900
does not have the responsibility of giving advice.

608
00:30:59,260 --> 00:31:00,500
Is it something new added to his job?

609
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:01,460
Well…

610
00:31:03,460 --> 00:31:04,260
It isn’t.

611
00:31:06,540 --> 00:31:08,940
Then, does Chen Hui

612
00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:11,300
hold a concurrent post of Censor

613
00:31:11,860 --> 00:31:12,900
who has the responsibility to supervise

614
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:14,500
and judge all the officials ?

615
00:31:21,100 --> 00:31:24,100
Chen Hui is not with the Censorate.

616
00:31:28,060 --> 00:31:29,580
Then Mr. Lv, tell me.

617
00:31:30,980 --> 00:31:32,220
Is the law of forbidding

618
00:31:32,780 --> 00:31:34,060
all officials

619
00:31:34,060 --> 00:31:35,620
to talk about issues out of their range

620
00:31:35,980 --> 00:31:37,220
abolished now?

621
00:31:41,900 --> 00:31:43,340
You must be joking now.

622
00:31:44,820 --> 00:31:46,540
Forbiddance of talking about issues out of range

623
00:31:46,540 --> 00:31:48,420
is an important measure of the court.

624
00:31:49,340 --> 00:31:50,700
It has been approved by His Majesty.

625
00:31:51,580 --> 00:31:53,340
How can we just abolish it?

626
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:57,380
Then does Chen Hui

627
00:31:57,980 --> 00:31:59,300
have the responsibility to impeach Cai Xiang

628
00:31:59,700 --> 00:32:02,100
and criticize the merits of officials
in the capital?

629
00:32:03,540 --> 00:32:05,420
If he’s just the Assistant Prefectural
Magistrate of Sizhou,

630
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:07,420
then of course not.

631
00:32:07,660 --> 00:32:08,580
Chen Hui

632
00:32:08,740 --> 00:32:10,220
has broken the law of the court.

633
00:32:11,060 --> 00:32:13,060
He speculated what His Majesty thinks

634
00:32:13,060 --> 00:32:13,940
after seeing the people Cai Xiang
praised in his poems

635
00:32:14,020 --> 00:32:15,220
being demoted

636
00:32:15,740 --> 00:32:17,380
to earn quick success and instant benefit.

637
00:32:17,700 --> 00:32:18,660
What a cunning sycophant!

638
00:32:19,340 --> 00:32:21,300
Cai Xiang humiliated

639
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:22,900
Censor Gao with frivolous words

640
00:32:23,020 --> 00:32:24,900
and disgraced the court.

641
00:32:26,460 --> 00:32:28,220
Cai Xiang was just complaining as a scholar.

642
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:30,700
What he did is nothing
more than frivolous behavior.

643
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:31,860
That is about his personal morality.

644
00:32:32,340 --> 00:32:33,340
While Chen Hui,

645
00:32:33,620 --> 00:32:35,260
as an official of the court,

646
00:32:35,540 --> 00:32:37,500
broke the law brazenly.

647
00:32:37,780 --> 00:32:38,900
He actually

648
00:32:39,100 --> 00:32:40,900
ruined the dignity of law.

649
00:32:43,340 --> 00:32:44,220
Your Highness,

650
00:32:44,740 --> 00:32:46,180
are the villains in Fan Zhongyan’s words

651
00:32:47,020 --> 00:32:50,220
the Prime Minister and Censor Gao?

652
00:32:54,380 --> 00:32:56,420
I do admire

653
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:58,180
his talent and character,

654
00:32:59,740 --> 00:33:01,300
but I don’t know much about politics,

655
00:33:01,820 --> 00:33:03,540
and dare not make any judgement on it.

656
00:33:06,580 --> 00:33:07,780
Recently,

657
00:33:08,980 --> 00:33:11,460
there are many ladies

658
00:33:11,460 --> 00:33:13,460
inviting my mom and sisters
to tea parties or poem parties.

659
00:33:14,700 --> 00:33:16,220
They gave my mom

660
00:33:17,180 --> 00:33:20,180
a lot of precious gifts

661
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:22,340
for me and my baby.

662
00:33:23,460 --> 00:33:25,740
They also talked a lot about the court,

663
00:33:26,620 --> 00:33:29,140
saying Fan Zhongyan is striving for reputation,

664
00:33:29,820 --> 00:33:31,900
Ouyang Xiu has moral flaws.

665
00:33:32,540 --> 00:33:33,820
And they asked

666
00:33:34,420 --> 00:33:36,820
if His Majesty told me

667
00:33:37,900 --> 00:33:39,900
how he thinks about this.

668
00:33:41,740 --> 00:33:43,620
My mother was his wet nurse,

669
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:46,340
but she never had contact with

670
00:33:46,340 --> 00:33:47,300
noble women.

671
00:33:48,900 --> 00:33:49,820
But now

672
00:33:51,900 --> 00:33:53,540
It must be for the baby.

673
00:33:58,940 --> 00:33:59,700
Your Highness,

674
00:34:02,020 --> 00:34:03,580
I’m really scared.

675
00:34:08,140 --> 00:34:10,020
You all made a good point.

676
00:34:11,260 --> 00:34:13,180
Both of them are wrong.

677
00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:15,060
But both are concerned about the country.

678
00:34:17,140 --> 00:34:18,300
No one is flawless.

679
00:34:18,700 --> 00:34:21,340
Don’t be too harsh on people
who made mistake for the first time.

680
00:34:22,300 --> 00:34:24,060
Let’s just end up here.

681
00:34:25,100 --> 00:34:25,900
In the future,

682
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:29,180
officials need to be cautious

683
00:34:29,340 --> 00:34:31,540
about their words and behaviors anywhere, anytime,

684
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:33,380
keep the dignity of the court in mind

685
00:34:33,540 --> 00:34:35,900
and do no frivolous things.

686
00:34:38,020 --> 00:34:39,740
You are absolutely right, Your Majesty.

687
00:34:40,780 --> 00:34:42,220
We understand.

688
00:34:42,580 --> 00:34:45,820
We’ll follow your instructions.

689
00:34:48,540 --> 00:34:49,980
It’s late now,

690
00:34:50,620 --> 00:34:53,340
do you have anything important
to discuss at the court?

691
00:34:58,580 --> 00:35:00,660
I have one thing.

692
00:35:03,980 --> 00:35:05,860
Soon

693
00:35:06,460 --> 00:35:08,060
you’ll have

694
00:35:08,060 --> 00:35:09,020
your first child.

695
00:35:09,780 --> 00:35:11,820
But Madam Miao, the boy’s mother,

696
00:35:11,940 --> 00:35:13,180
is not of high ranking.

697
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:15,540
She is just the Lady of Renshou County.

698
00:35:16,340 --> 00:35:17,220
This seems…

699
00:35:17,860 --> 00:35:19,380
Madam Miao comes from a good family.

700
00:35:20,060 --> 00:35:21,460
Her mother was my wet nurse,

701
00:35:21,900 --> 00:35:23,140
who made contribution to the royal family

702
00:35:23,380 --> 00:35:24,940
and has been given the title
of the mother of State Qi.

703
00:35:25,420 --> 00:35:26,220
When Miao was young,

704
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:28,580
she was taught by Her Majesty.

705
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:31,500
She is clever, sensible, virtuous and gentle.

706
00:35:31,940 --> 00:35:32,980
She’s been in the palace for 6 years.

707
00:35:33,220 --> 00:35:34,340
She served Her Majesty

708
00:35:34,340 --> 00:35:35,500
and two Empresses.

709
00:35:35,540 --> 00:35:36,820
She made no mistakes.

710
00:35:37,620 --> 00:35:38,540
Why doesn’t she deserve to be

711
00:35:38,620 --> 00:35:39,740
the mother of my first son?

712
00:35:40,540 --> 00:35:41,740
You are right, Your Majesty.

713
00:35:42,020 --> 00:35:44,300
Madam Miao should’ve been promoted long ago.

714
00:35:45,020 --> 00:35:47,060
Don’t aggrieve the first son of Your Majesty

715
00:35:47,180 --> 00:35:48,100
because of

716
00:35:48,100 --> 00:35:49,740
her modesty.

717
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:51,140
I believe

718
00:35:51,620 --> 00:35:55,140
Madam Miao should be promoted
to Zhaoyi (a title of concubines).

719
00:36:05,940 --> 00:36:08,620
She should be promoted.

720
00:36:10,260 --> 00:36:12,980
But the promotion of concubines

721
00:36:14,020 --> 00:36:16,300
should be handled by inner court

722
00:36:16,420 --> 00:36:18,100
= Wang Zeng, courtesy name Xiaoxian =
to review their merits,

723
00:36:18,420 --> 00:36:20,140
refer to previous cases

724
00:36:20,620 --> 00:36:22,740
and report to His Majesty.

725
00:36:23,860 --> 00:36:25,060
After His Majesty decided,

726
00:36:25,540 --> 00:36:26,660
the announcement will be made.

727
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:29,340
I think Mr. Lv

728
00:36:29,700 --> 00:36:32,660
crossed the line, making a decision

729
00:36:33,340 --> 00:36:35,820
of the promotion in the harem.

730
00:36:41,140 --> 00:36:42,740
Concubines with children

731
00:36:43,980 --> 00:36:45,500
will have more trouble

732
00:36:45,980 --> 00:36:47,540
than those without.

733
00:36:49,380 --> 00:36:51,820
The more you have counted on others,

734
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:54,260
the more trouble and danger you will get.

735
00:36:55,740 --> 00:36:56,740
But

736
00:36:57,340 --> 00:36:59,500
don’t you feel happy

737
00:36:59,900 --> 00:37:00,580
to be the first woman

738
00:37:01,140 --> 00:37:02,820
who has a child with His Majesty?

739
00:37:02,820 --> 00:37:03,860
Don’t you feel joyful?

740
00:37:05,340 --> 00:37:06,540
Of course.

741
00:37:07,980 --> 00:37:12,740
But I got more and more worries recently.

742
00:37:13,220 --> 00:37:14,020
Xinhe,

743
00:37:15,460 --> 00:37:16,860
you are gentle and sincere,

744
00:37:17,380 --> 00:37:18,820
also know how people think.

745
00:37:19,940 --> 00:37:21,220
That’s why you are blessed

746
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:23,500
with his first child.

747
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:26,580
As for the disturbance from outside,

748
00:37:27,140 --> 00:37:29,140
just ignore them.

749
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,460
As long as you

750
00:37:31,980 --> 00:37:32,900
love His Majesty,

751
00:37:33,740 --> 00:37:36,180
you behave well,

752
00:37:36,980 --> 00:37:39,260
don’t you believe His Majesty will trust you

753
00:37:39,540 --> 00:37:40,460
and protect you?

754
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:46,660
I believe you too, Your Highness.

755
00:37:52,580 --> 00:37:54,660
= Su Shunqin, courtesy name Zimei =
Mr. Han is the most eloquent and clever man.

756
00:37:55,060 --> 00:37:57,100
The forbiddance they issued

757
00:37:57,100 --> 00:37:59,780
to shut up officials’ mouth

758
00:37:59,900 --> 00:38:01,900
is used by Mr. Han

759
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:02,900
on themselves too,

760
00:38:03,060 --> 00:38:04,020
destroying Xia Song’s plan

761
00:38:04,140 --> 00:38:05,980
about using his subordinate’s words

762
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:08,260
to persecute Cai Junmo and control public opinions.

763
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:10,020
What a clever move!

764
00:38:12,260 --> 00:38:14,980
Unfortunately I only have a low ranking
and stood too far behind.

765
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:17,100
I was unable to see Lv Yijian’s face.

766
00:38:17,580 --> 00:38:19,020
Lv Yijian is sophisticated enough

767
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:20,860
to hide his temper

768
00:38:21,060 --> 00:38:22,340
in his heart.

769
00:38:22,940 --> 00:38:24,180
I didn’t see anything

770
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:27,500
but I guess he didn’t show anything on his face.

771
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:30,540
Yanguo is right.

772
00:38:31,300 --> 00:38:33,100
Zimei, you underestimated Lv Yijian.

773
00:38:33,860 --> 00:38:34,620
Today

774
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,500
he used the promotion of Madam Miao

775
00:38:36,500 --> 00:38:37,540
to counteract.

776
00:38:38,180 --> 00:38:39,060
That is a smart move.

777
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:40,220
Smart indeed.

778
00:38:40,900 --> 00:38:42,020
I was surprised that

779
00:38:42,220 --> 00:38:43,180
he wasn’t worried about

780
00:38:43,180 --> 00:38:44,300
the accusation of colluding with concubines at all.

781
00:38:44,700 --> 00:38:45,540
What an arrogant man.

782
00:38:45,940 --> 00:38:47,260
Extremely arrogant and arbitrary.

783
00:38:49,100 --> 00:38:49,700
Zimei,

784
00:38:50,460 --> 00:38:51,940
don’t forget the life story of His Majesty.

785
00:38:57,180 --> 00:39:00,740
= Hall of Peace =

786
00:39:05,300 --> 00:39:07,460
Are you reading medical books?

787
00:39:07,860 --> 00:39:09,060
We have so many physicians.

788
00:39:12,180 --> 00:39:13,460
I am worried.

789
00:39:14,300 --> 00:39:15,340
After all this is his

790
00:39:15,420 --> 00:39:16,340
first son

791
00:39:17,260 --> 00:39:18,900
and the first

792
00:39:19,500 --> 00:39:20,780
since I became the Empress.

793
00:39:21,700 --> 00:39:22,620
His Majesty is here.

794
00:39:30,260 --> 00:39:30,900
Danshu,

795
00:39:31,500 --> 00:39:32,460
give me some

796
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:33,740
desserts you kept.

797
00:39:34,460 --> 00:39:35,860
You just came back from the court

798
00:39:35,860 --> 00:39:36,820
and didn’t have lunch?

799
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:39,620
I came here directly after work.

800
00:39:41,300 --> 00:39:42,060
I don’t know how much

801
00:39:42,700 --> 00:39:43,780
breakfast they ate

802
00:39:43,780 --> 00:39:44,820
in the morning.

803
00:39:45,060 --> 00:39:46,180
It’s over 12 p.m. already,

804
00:39:46,500 --> 00:39:47,820
but they were still

805
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:49,220
fighting against each other at the court.

806
00:39:49,580 --> 00:39:50,500
If I didn’t dismiss them,

807
00:39:50,700 --> 00:39:51,620
I wouldn’t be able to tell

808
00:39:51,620 --> 00:39:52,820
who was arguing with whom.

809
00:40:03,260 --> 00:40:04,020
It’s hot.

810
00:40:05,020 --> 00:40:05,700
Slow down.

811
00:40:21,380 --> 00:40:22,420
Xinhe made this, right?

812
00:40:22,980 --> 00:40:24,380
The taste is unique.

813
00:40:26,060 --> 00:40:27,860
You are so perspicacious

814
00:40:27,940 --> 00:40:29,700
even when eating desserts.

815
00:40:30,860 --> 00:40:32,580
Xinhe gave these to me.

816
00:40:36,500 --> 00:40:38,420
I haven’t received

817
00:40:38,420 --> 00:40:39,220
any dessert

818
00:40:39,220 --> 00:40:40,900
from the Pavilion of Phoenix for long.

819
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:42,940
Now I know

820
00:40:43,620 --> 00:40:44,660
Danshu is the one in charge

821
00:40:45,100 --> 00:40:46,340
in the harem.

822
00:40:48,300 --> 00:40:49,420
Officials are all clinging to

823
00:40:49,460 --> 00:40:51,020
the Prime Minister,

824
00:40:51,380 --> 00:40:52,340
while concubines in the harem

825
00:40:52,340 --> 00:40:53,580
are also pretty realistic.

826
00:40:58,780 --> 00:41:00,020
Lv Yijian is smart indeed.

827
00:41:01,140 --> 00:41:03,220
He hit His Majesty directly

828
00:41:03,220 --> 00:41:04,500
by saying the mother of his child
is not of high ranking

829
00:41:04,500 --> 00:41:06,060
and found out his opinion on this immediately.

830
00:41:06,060 --> 00:41:07,540
Then he just followed his opinion

831
00:41:07,540 --> 00:41:09,820
and proposed to promote Madam Miao.

832
00:41:11,460 --> 00:41:12,900
Lv Yijian has many people in the inner court,

833
00:41:13,260 --> 00:41:14,060
the news will be spread

834
00:41:14,300 --> 00:41:15,340
